Returns the parameters the distribution was constructed with.

@1@ Returns the {{math|m}} (the first degree of freedom) distribution parameter. The default value is {{c|1.0}}.

@2@ Returns the {{math|n}} (the second degree of freedom) distribution parameter. The default value is {{c|1.0}}.

===Parameters===
(none)

===Return value===
@1@ The {{math|m}} (the first degree of freedom) distribution parameter.

@2@ The {{math|n}} (the second degree of freedom) distribution parameter. 

===Complexity===
Constant.
